title: Timmy Missions: Mexico
description: "Timmy Missions" is a web series created to showcase all of Timmy's travels. This episode consists of Timmy in his home away from home, MEXICO. The waves Timmy score in the first segment are probably the best the points down there have ever gotten. Timmy Reyes traveled alone side good friend and filmer Tony Adams to document the whole experience. Have at it!
